<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Beddington Heights</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Named after the Town of Beddington located in Surrey, England, the community in Beddington Heights is one of the largest in the area boasting of a north of 12500 residential units.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given its northern location within the city, close proximity to schools and shopping complexes and affordable housing options, <span class="par-xl">Beddington Heights homes for sale are a popular choice for most first time homebuyers and investors alike</span>.</p>
        </div>
